title: [BUG] Nami Taunt Overlap
body:
It's not a MAJOR bug, 
but recently I've noticed when I taunt with Nami, 
her base fish overlays her urf fish, 
*The top right fish* He has fins and a mouth in his neck XD 

At first i thought, oh, they gave one of her fish fins, hes a lil shark urf :3 
then i realised he had a neckmouth XD and it had overlapped xD x

replies.body:
Hiya LightSwiftWolf,

Thanks for the report! We're aware of the issue and are working on a fix.

great ^^ 
im a support main and i feel like ive supported the community! ;D
